	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" Mario can keep a power-up in reserve, similar to how Super Mario World works except the change is immediately effective.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" There is a new power-up, Magic Mario, which can stomp on more enemies than otherwise possible, shoots extremely powerful projectiles, and can take a few hits before losing the power-up.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" There are 7 worlds which Mario can visit in any order. Each world has a key hidden somewhere within it.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" After finding all 7 keys and beating the 7 worlds, Mario can access the 8th world to win the game.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Almost all levels end with a Boom-Boom battle.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Mario Adventure includes its own custom palette for graphics rendering.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
